<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Taylor Hill was among the glamorous arrivals on the red carpet for the opening ceremony of the socially distanced 77th Venice Film Festival.</p>

<p>The model, 24, looked stunning in a cut-out skin-baring gown as she attended the Lacci red carpet in the Italian city on Wednesday evening.</p>

<p>Taylor cut an elegant figure in the paisley print dress in hues of pink and purple, which she adorned with a selection of dazzling jewels.</p>

<p>Leading the way: Taylor Hill was among the glamorous arrivals on the red carpet for the opening ceremony of the socially distanced 77th Venice Film Festiva</p>

<p>Taylor wore her brunette locks up in a chic plaited up do, while enhancing her striking features with a heavy pallet of make-up in bronze tones. </p>

